org.apereo.cas.services

Interface RegisteredServiceAttributeReleasePolicy

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public interface RegisteredServiceAttributeReleasePolicy
extends java.io.Serializable
    The release policy that decides how attributes are to be released for a given service. Each policy has the ability to apply an optional filter.
    Since:
    4.1.0
